><br />\n疑似後宮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">毒品</span><br />\n四月是你的謊言<br />\n白色相簿2<br />\n來自風平浪靜的明日<br />\n偽戀<br />\n只有我不存在的城市<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">喜歡純愛者不推薦</span><br />\n家有女友<br />\n人渣本願<br />\n戀愛與謊言"},{"pid":"4072b94f81bc2046ba0131163ba88c39c14f14e9","tid":2105682,"uid":318495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"戀如雨止"},{"pid":"a370a6d3f579c36276b622e7d723c524f2d3fc65","tid":2105682,"uid":208196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:34:59.000Z","msg":"迷之女友 超甜"},{"pid":"c7662dba08904f688796b8af0a2f035214cb00ac","tid":2105682,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:55:23.000Z","msg":"小鎮有你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61271ed186c334d6b41dadacdb8013a18502a562","tid":2105682,"uid":6142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7662dba08904f688796b8af0a2f035214cb00ac","tid":2105682,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:55:23.000Z","msg":"小鎮有你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:16:36.000Z","msg":"果陣漫畫追live<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf24fe7b752c74799c2483f25fd24ac68fd6b9be","tid":2105682,"uid":313435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be5ba48c5903f69260e8e0bac926e30c9fdfff8b","tid":2105682,"uid":217942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:20:28.000Z","msg":"出租女友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T22:47:43.000Z","msg":"成個七月所有系嘅動畫都有出租女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd06a7c6778c2790cb11e9ca22260e3d4ebe517","tid":2105682,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61271ed186c334d6b41dadacdb8013a